Privacy Policy для FitCoach
Introduction

Our privacy policy will help you understand what information we collect at FitCoach, how FitCoach uses it, and what choices you have.
FitCoach is a fitness app designed for personal users and fitness trainers. This SERVICE is provided by FitCoach at no cost and is intended for use as is.
By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. The Personal Information we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, accessible on our website, unless otherwise defined here.
Information Collection and Use
To provide a better experience while using our Service, we may require you to provide certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to: name, email address, gender, location, profile pictures, and fitness-related data (workouts, progress photos, goals). The information we collect is retained and used as described in this policy.
The app may use third-party services that could collect information to identify you.

Cookies
Cookies are files with small amounts of data commonly used as anonymous unique identifiers. They are sent to your browser from the websites you visit and stored on your device.
FitCoach does not use cookies explicitly. However, third-party services or libraries integrated into the app may use cookies to collect information and improve services. You can choose to accept or refuse cookies, but some parts of the Service may not function properly if refused.

Location Information
Some features may use location information from your device. We only use this data within the scope necessary for providing the relevant services (for example, trainer search by location).

Device Information
We may collect information from your device for providing better service, analytics, and fraud prevention. This information does not include personally identifiable information unless explicitly provided by you.

Service Providers
We may employ third-party companies and individuals for the following reasons:

To facilitate the Service;
To provide the Service on our behalf;
To perform Service-related tasks; or
To assist in analyzing how our Service is used.
These third parties have access to your Personal Information solely to perform tasks assigned to them and are obligated not to use it for other purposes.

Security
We value your trust and strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information. However, no method of transmission or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Delete Account
You can delete your account by navigating to the "Settings" screen within the app. Once selected, your account and associated data will be permanently deleted. Account recovery is not provided after deletion.

Children’s Privacy
This Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided personal information, it is immediately deleted. Parents or guardians who become aware that their child has shared information can contact us for necessary action.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. You are advised to review this page for changes. Updates are effective immediately upon posting.

Contact Us
